title: 5th Annual Alumni Golf Outing (10/10/2015)
text: 10/10/2015 Event Description Get your team ready and join us for this year's Alumni Golf Outing! Network with fellow alumni and friends on a fun fall day at the golf course. You'll have   gift card, two tickets to a 2015 PSU Football game, and other random prizes. Beat the Penn College Golf Coach Competition and mulligans to benefit the Wildcat Golf team.$65 per golfer/$260 per foursomeincludes greens fees, lunch catered by Le Jeune Chef, and prizes for first, second, and last place team and for closest to the pin and longest drive. Net proceeds   Scholarship Fund.
